it will be unconditionally.

494
00:40:47,280 --> 00:40:50,079
You see? See how they've changed you?

495
00:40:50,159 --> 00:40:53,559
Dad, maybe I haven't changed.

496
00:40:55,559 --> 00:40:57,440
Maybe the old Nadia wasn't me.

497
00:40:58,320 --> 00:41:01,920
She was a girl who tried
to please her parents above all.

498
00:41:03,400 --> 00:41:05,000
Maybe I'm different.

499
00:41:07,719 --> 00:41:09,119
Like your sister?

500
00:41:09,239 --> 00:41:10,079
No.

501
00:41:11,320 --> 00:41:15,119
I don't know who I am yet.
But I'm going to find out.

502
00:41:15,679 --> 00:41:19,920
I hope you and Mom can accept it
and love me.

503
00:41:20,920 --> 00:41:23,440
But I'm going to be myself, Dad. Myself.

504
00:41:35,800 --> 00:41:37,360
We know who killed her.

505
00:41:38,880 --> 00:41:41,639
On the first of June, around 9:30 p.m.,

506
00:41:42,079 --> 00:41:43,920
you entered the school pool.

507
00:41:45,400 --> 00:41:46,679
Marina was there.

508
00:41:48,119 --> 00:41:50,639
You had an increasingly heated argument...

509
00:41:51,079 --> 00:41:52,639
until you picked up the trophy,

510
00:41:52,719 --> 00:41:54,920
and hit her
in the back of the head with it.

511
00:41:56,800 --> 00:41:58,159
She did not die instantly,

512
00:41:58,239 --> 00:42:00,800
which means you left her there,
bleeding to death.

513
00:42:01,639 --> 00:42:02,960
Come with me, please.

514
00:42:09,159 --> 00:42:11,320
This is what we believe happened,

515
00:42:11,400 --> 00:42:13,159
and, more importantly,

516
00:42:13,719 --> 00:42:15,679
what the judge believes happened.

517
00:42:29,440 --> 00:42:32,719
You'd save us a lot of work if you told us
where to find the murder weapon,

518
00:42:32,800 --> 00:42:33,800
the trophy.

519
00:42:38,639 --> 00:42:40,039
Oh, right,

520
00:42:40,360 --> 00:42:42,840
you don't have a shred of evidence.
Nothing.

521
00:42:43,519 --> 00:42:44,360
It's him.

522
00:42:44,880 --> 00:42:47,400
You're under arrest
for the murder of Marina Nunier.

523
