-What?
-Hold him tight.

524
00:42:49,239 --> 00:42:52,199
What the fuck are you saying?

525
00:42:52,320 --> 00:42:54,519
-Grab him!
-What the hell are you saying?

526
00:42:54,599 --> 00:42:56,599
Look me in the face and say it again!

527
00:42:56,719 --> 00:42:58,840
We have a witness, your brother.

528
00:42:59,239 --> 00:43:00,159
A motive.

529
00:43:00,480 --> 00:43:03,559
As her messages prove,
she'd changed her mind about running away.

530
00:43:03,639 --> 00:43:04,880
That's why you killed her.

531
00:43:04,960 --> 00:43:08,480
Samu! You know I'd never hurt Marina.

532
00:43:08,559 --> 00:43:11,159
-Get him!
-You know I'd never hurt Marina, Samu!

533
00:43:11,239 --> 00:43:12,519
They killed her for that watch.

534
00:43:12,599 --> 00:43:16,880
The pen¬†drive had a lot of dirt
