565
00:45:18,639 --> 00:45:21,159
You've been told so many times
that you own the world

566
00:45:21,239 --> 00:45:23,039
that you actually believe it, huh?

567
00:45:26,760 --> 00:45:28,239
See you in class, Lucrecia.

568
00:45:29,079 --> 00:45:30,599
That's if they let you go back.

569
00:45:54,840 --> 00:45:55,679
Guzm√°n.

