597
00:48:15,159 --> 00:48:17,599
-You are not to blame for anything.
-I accused him.

598
00:48:18,119 --> 00:48:20,320
-And he's not guilty.
-I know.

599
00:48:20,800 --> 00:48:23,199
There must be a way to prove
it wasn't him.

600
00:48:24,000 --> 00:48:26,280
Even if we had seen the murderer
with our own eyes,

